hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: We were at school together aboutkidshealth.ca Doherty provided security and surveillance for the show's production team as it chased in one case a well-known financier of the 9/11 attacks through the streets of Hamburg. Doherty talks about the car chases and how he managed to stay awake on stake-outs and discusses his impressions of his friends Adam, Roger and Scott, whom he protected on those shoots. The video is being shown with the permission of Doherty's mother, Barbara, to provide insight into who Doherty was and why the nation should honor his service.Â
